---
title: Korean-Style Chicken & Charred Corn Slaw with Sriracha Mayo
description: If you’re having sticky glazed chicken then you will need a handy-dandy slaw to go with them. A charred corn slaw, drizzled in a punchy sriracha mayo and tossed through with veggies and spring onion is the perfect slaw for the job. It’s a winning combination!

*This recipe is under 550kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
